N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 462.1 - Scope

State Regulations

This Part applies to the provision of nonresidential
services for victims of domestic violence by social services districts directly
or pursuant to purchase of services contracts with not-for-profit
organizations. Notes
